    <item>
      <title>中国将于年底前就毛泽东时代非洲铁路的特许经营权达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/china-to-agree-concession-for-mao-era-africa-railway-by-year-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该铁路主管部门称，一家中国国有企业将在 2024 年底前完成协议，接管连接赞比亚铜矿至坦桑尼亚港口的铁路特许权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/china-to-agree-concession-for-mao-era-africa-railway-by-year-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席财务官表示消费者压力大、业绩不佳，Ally 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/ally-drops-after-cfo-flags-consumer-stress-underperformance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ally Financial Inc. 的首席财务官 Russ Hutchinson 强调其借款人的信用恶化情况加剧，并表示这家汽车贷款机构可能会表现不佳，随后该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/ally-drops-after-cfo-flags-consumer-stress-underperformance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:28:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通收入乐观情绪减弱，银行股领跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-shares-slide-as-pinto-says-analysts-are-too-optimistic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司总裁丹尼尔平托表示，分析师对明年的支出和净利息收入的预测过于乐观，导致该行股价出现四年多来最大跌幅，引领银行股走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-shares-slide-as-pinto-says-analysts-are-too-optimistic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:28:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应过剩担忧加剧 布伦特原油跌破 70 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brent-oil-tumbles-below-70-as-oversupply-fears-deepen-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布伦特原油期货自 2021 年 12 月以来首次跌破每桶 70 美元，这是由于供应充足、需求担忧和投机性抛售猖獗而引发的价格暴跌导致的又一次下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brent-oil-tumbles-below-70-as-oversupply-fears-deepen-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行称全球贸易变化可能推高价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bank-of-canada-says-global-trade-shifts-may-drive-up-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆表示，全球贸易趋势的变化可能会在未来带来更多的供应冲击，从而可能推高价格并增加通胀的波动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bank-of-canada-says-global-trade-shifts-may-drive-up-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马刹车召回和大众裁员威胁加剧德国工业危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车制造商正陷入更深的危机，损害该国最重要行业的未来，宝马汽车公司警告称，利润将受到代价高昂的刹车问题的冲击，大众汽车公司则取消了员工三十年来享受的就业保障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应风险缓解，欧洲天然气价格跌至五周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/european-gas-prices-push-higher-as-cold-snap-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于可再生能源发电量增加和燃料消费量疲软帮助市场在供暖季来临前平静下来，欧洲天然气价格跌至 8 月初以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/european-gas-prices-push-higher-as-cold-snap-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马下调业绩预期后，汽车股领跌欧洲股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/rebound-in-european-stocks-fizzles-out-before-us-inflation-ecb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市下跌，汽车板块因宝马下调业绩预期领跌。美国通胀数据和欧洲央行会议公布前，投资者也持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/rebound-in-european-stocks-fizzles-out-before-us-inflation-ecb</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型银行拉响警报，标普 500 指数涨势受阻：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街几家大型银行对前景持谨慎态度，导致股市受到冲击。由于供应过剩担忧加剧，布伦特原油跌至每桶 70 美元以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 22:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
